    • getBestInterlinearMode

      InterlinearMode getBestInterlinearMode(String mainBook, List<String> extraVersions, InterlinearMode interlinearMode)
      Determines the best interlinear mode available for the given versions. The order of preference is

      INTERLINEAR INTERLEAVED_COMPARE INTERLEAVED

      Parameters:
      mainBook - the main book
      extraVersions - the extra versions
      interlinearMode -
      Returns:
      the best interlinear mode.
